vjni
Class Vjni

java.lang.Object
  vjni.Vjni

public class Vjni
extends java.lang.Object

this class serves as the interface between VGI and Vaucanson Library; for this class to work, the vaucanson vjni.so file must be provided in the static section; for what each functions does, refer to vaucanson library user manuals
